1
00:01:02,280 --> 00:01:03,360
That's not right.

2
00:01:03,920 --> 00:01:05,480
The Zhang Shisan we saw

3
00:01:05,680 --> 00:01:07,280
had perfectly fine fingers.

4
00:01:07,280 --> 00:01:09,480
Could the old lady have remembered it wrong?

5
00:01:09,480 --> 00:01:10,340
It's possible.

6
00:01:10,600 --> 00:01:12,400
It has been ten years, after all.

7
00:01:16,560 --> 00:01:17,800
Is it possible that

8
00:01:21,160 --> 00:01:22,800
the one the old crab seller talked about

9
00:01:22,800 --> 00:01:24,260
and the Zhang Shisan we saw

10
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:26,660
are not the same person at all?

11
00:01:28,800 --> 00:01:30,660
That there are two Zhang Shisans?

12
00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:34,080
Also, I think there's something strange about that grandfather and grandson.

13
00:01:34,080 --> 00:01:36,600
If Zhang Jinxi really loves Zhang Shisan,

14
00:01:36,920 --> 00:01:38,580
why does he watch him every day

15
00:01:38,800 --> 00:01:40,660
and never let him leave the house?

16
00:01:41,039 --> 00:01:43,700
When we checked Zhang Shisan's room yesterday,

17
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:45,720
there was something strange.

18
00:01:47,039 --> 00:01:49,280
If Zhang Shisan ran away on his own,

19
00:01:49,720 --> 00:01:51,650
why was the vase in the room broken?

20
00:01:52,360 --> 00:01:54,690
If Zhang Shisan didn't run away on his own,

21
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:57,120
then he must have had an altercation with someone.

22
00:01:57,120 --> 00:01:59,250
He might have been taken away by force.

23
00:02:06,960 --> 00:02:07,690
Brother Bao.

24
00:02:09,199 --> 00:02:10,800
Where are the people from Kangren Noodle Shop?

25
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:12,600
The shop has been closed all day.

26
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:13,880
They should all be inside.

27
00:02:13,880 --> 00:02:15,140
They haven't come out.

28
00:02:40,240 --> 00:02:41,360
Search every room.

29
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:42,079
Yes, sir.

30
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:46,040
He ran away at a time like this.

31
00:02:46,040 --> 00:02:49,100
There is definitely something wrong with Zhang Jinxi.

32
00:02:58,520 --> 00:03:00,120
These two pomegranate trees,

33
00:03:00,120 --> 00:03:01,440
why is one fine,

34
00:03:01,640 --> 00:03:02,840
but the other is dead?

35
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:05,930
Besides, they run a business here.

36
00:03:07,040 --> 00:03:08,700
Keeping a dead tree right here

37
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:10,250
doesn't make sense.

38
00:03:12,320 --> 00:03:13,320
Do you remember

39
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:15,400
the mud on He Xiaolian?

40
00:04:19,959 --> 00:04:21,800
These female bodies in cheongsams

41
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:23,400
all have one thing in common.

42
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:27,000
There are fractures on the sternum caused by the tip of a knife.

43
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:28,200
The blade marks are deeper on the left, shallower on the right,

44
00:04:28,200 --> 00:04:29,330
and very irregular.

45
00:04:29,880 --> 00:04:31,280
We can confirm they were caused

46
00:04:31,280 --> 00:04:33,520
by the forcible removal of an organ.

47
00:04:33,920 --> 00:04:35,200
Judging by the location,

48
00:04:35,200 --> 00:04:36,460
it must be the stomach.

49
00:04:36,960 --> 00:04:39,080
It seems they're all like He Xiaolian.

50
00:04:39,080 --> 00:04:42,080
Their stomachs were cut out because of leaking opium.

51
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:44,040
The clothes on this male body.

52
00:04:44,320 --> 00:04:46,250
It looks a lot like Zhang Shisan's,

53
00:04:46,760 --> 00:04:48,720
but his bones are already calcified.

54
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:49,560
This means

55
00:04:50,040 --> 00:04:52,200
he's been dead for at least five years.

56
00:04:52,960 --> 00:04:54,890
Look at the bones of his right hand.

57
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:58,680
The pinky finger is missing two joints.

58
00:04:58,760 --> 00:04:59,760
This is the Zhang Shisan

59
00:04:59,760 --> 00:05:01,760
that the old crab-selling lady saw.

60
00:05:01,760 --> 00:05:03,360
It must be that after he died,

61
00:05:03,760 --> 00:05:04,800
Zhang Jinxi started using the current

62
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:06,460
Zhang Shisan as a body double.

63
00:05:07,280 --> 00:05:08,560
It seems Zhang Shisan

64
00:05:08,880 --> 00:05:10,340
didn't run away on his own,

65
00:05:10,960 --> 00:05:13,160
but was forcibly taken by Zhang Jinxi.

66
00:05:13,760 --> 00:05:15,760
Because once we find Zhang Shisan,

67
00:05:16,200 --> 00:05:18,660
all of Zhang Jinxi's crimes will be exposed.

68
00:05:18,840 --> 00:05:19,880
So,

69
00:05:19,880 --> 00:05:22,400
Zhang Jinxi not only killed this boy

70
00:05:22,400 --> 00:05:24,000
and kidnapped Zhang Shisan,

71
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:26,200
but also caused the deaths of the girls

72
00:05:26,200 --> 00:05:28,240
who had accidents carrying drugs inside them.

73
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:29,800
Zhang Jinxi must be

74
00:05:29,800 --> 00:05:32,400
the mastermind behind the opium trafficking.

75
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:37,720
We searched for a long time again,

76
00:05:37,720 --> 00:05:39,640
but still couldn't find Zhang Jinxi.

77
00:05:39,640 --> 00:05:40,200
However,

78
00:05:40,200 --> 00:05:41,800
I asked the Concession guards,

79
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:43,760
and they said Zhang Jinxi hasn't left the Concession.

80
00:05:43,760 --> 00:05:46,440
They must still be hiding in the French Concession.

81
00:05:46,440 --> 00:05:47,440
It's very likely.

82
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:48,800
Inform Inspector Zhang immediately

83
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:50,320
to start a full search in the Concession.

84
00:05:50,320 --> 00:05:50,850
Yes, sir.

85
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:56,640
Have you seen this person?

86
00:05:56,640 --> 00:05:57,360
No.

87
00:05:57,760 --> 00:05:58,320
No.

88
00:05:58,760 --> 00:06:00,220
Have you seen this person?

89
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:00,640
No.

90
00:06:01,320 --> 00:06:02,040
No.

91
00:06:04,640 --> 00:06:05,280
Have you seen him?

92
00:06:05,280 --> 00:06:05,840
No.

93
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:06,570
Let's go.

94
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:13,320
Look.

95
00:06:13,680 --> 00:06:17,040
I remember this building had a cholera outbreak six months ago.

96
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:18,900
The residents were all moved out.

97
00:06:19,440 --> 00:06:21,600
It should have been abandoned a long time ago.

98
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:23,460
Why are there people living here?

99
00:06:31,960 --> 00:06:32,560
Help!

100
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:34,360
Help!

101
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:46,280
Stop!

102
00:07:12,400 --> 00:07:12,920
Freeze!

103
00:07:12,960 --> 00:07:13,880
Or I'll shoot!

104
00:07:29,880 --> 00:07:31,080
Where is Zhang Jinxi?

105
00:07:41,360 --> 00:07:42,040
He's dead.

106
00:08:02,840 --> 00:08:05,080
Is life really so cheap?

107
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:14,240
How is my brother?

108
00:08:15,200 --> 00:08:16,040
Your brother?

109
00:08:16,640 --> 00:08:17,770
I mean Zhang Shisan.

110
00:08:18,080 --> 00:08:18,920
I went looking for him yesterday

111
00:08:18,920 --> 00:08:20,120
and found he was gone.

112
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:21,920
Isn't he here with you?

113
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:29,280
Zhang Jinxi, that bastard.

114
00:08:31,520 --> 00:08:34,360
So Zhang Jinxi was using you to traffic drugs?

115
00:08:34,679 --> 00:08:37,200
After the drugs inside He Xiaolian leaked,

116
00:08:37,200 --> 00:08:38,280
he killed her

117
00:08:38,280 --> 00:08:40,080
and buried her in his backyard.

118
00:08:40,240 --> 00:08:40,679
Right?

119
00:08:42,760 --> 00:08:43,440
Shisan must have been

120
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:45,040
locked up by that old geezer.

121
00:08:46,280 --> 00:08:46,960
Locked up?

122
00:08:47,520 --> 00:08:48,160
Where?

123
00:08:49,760 --> 00:08:50,480
The cell.

124
00:08:51,640 --> 00:08:52,960
It must be that cell.

125
00:08:56,800 --> 00:08:58,460
Do you know where this cell is?

126
00:08:59,480 --> 00:09:01,480
I was locked up there for a long time.

127
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:04,160
But I don't know where it is.

128
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:07,400
I just remember it was very damp.

129
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:10,640
And there was no light all year round.

130
00:09:11,680 --> 00:09:12,440
Haitang.

131
00:09:13,120 --> 00:09:14,920
If you want to save Zhang Shisan,

132
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:16,480
the only thing you can do now

133
00:09:16,480 --> 00:09:18,360
is to tell us everything you know,

134
00:09:18,360 --> 00:09:19,800
every single detail.

135
00:09:21,800 --> 00:09:22,640
Actually,

136
00:09:23,240 --> 00:09:25,300
Shisan isn't my biological brother.

137
00:09:26,920 --> 00:09:28,000
He and I,

138
00:09:28,720 --> 00:09:30,000
and Xiaolian too,

139
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:33,090
were all tricked into coming here by Zhang Jinxi.

140
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:35,930
Three years ago,

141
00:09:36,360 --> 00:09:38,220
there was a plague in my hometown,

142
00:09:38,400 --> 00:09:39,960
and my family all died.

143
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:43,040
I managed to escape to Shanghai.

144
00:09:43,800 --> 00:09:45,240
I was robbed by bandits on the way

145
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:46,400
and hurt my leg.

146
00:09:47,800 --> 00:09:49,400
No one was willing to hire me.

147
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:06,640
Child,

148
00:10:07,360 --> 00:10:09,890
if you don't grab some, there'll be none left.

149
00:10:09,960 --> 00:10:11,020
Aren't you hungry?

150
00:10:12,440 --> 00:10:14,280
I ate yesterday.

151
00:10:14,640 --> 00:10:16,680
They haven't eaten for days.

152
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:22,880
I can take you to the factory.

153
00:10:23,400 --> 00:10:24,200
Will you go?

154
00:10:57,040 --> 00:10:57,900
Where is the...

155
00:10:58,320 --> 00:10:59,160
Where is the...

156
00:10:59,160 --> 00:11:00,680
Where is the factory we were promised?

157
00:11:00,680 --> 00:11:01,680
Where is everyone?

158
00:11:01,680 --> 00:11:03,160
Where on earth did they go?

159
00:11:03,640 --> 00:11:04,840
Where's the factory?

160
00:11:04,960 --> 00:11:05,920
Where's everyone?

161
00:11:05,920 --> 00:11:07,240
Where did they all go?

162
00:11:07,240 --> 00:11:08,100
Stop shouting.

163
00:11:09,320 --> 00:11:10,450
They can't hear you.

164
00:11:15,160 --> 00:11:16,160
Drink some water.

165
00:11:16,320 --> 00:11:17,720
You won't feel so hungry.

166
00:11:23,800 --> 00:11:25,060
My name is He Xiaolian.

167
00:11:26,200 --> 00:11:27,560
Just call me Xiaolian.

168
00:11:28,400 --> 00:11:29,200
They said

169
00:11:29,680 --> 00:11:31,480
if we hold on for two more months,

170
00:11:31,560 --> 00:11:33,280
we can get out.

171
00:11:34,240 --> 00:11:35,120
Once we're out,

172
00:11:35,120 --> 00:11:36,880
we'll have a good life.

173
00:11:41,120 --> 00:11:42,080
My name is

174
00:11:42,880 --> 00:11:44,200
Qiao Haitang.

175
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:53,840
Xiaowu,

176
00:11:54,040 --> 00:11:55,970
why did you sneak out to play again?

177
00:12:07,080 --> 00:12:08,200
He is Zhang Shisan.

178
00:12:10,400 --> 00:12:11,920
Xiaolian told me

179
00:12:11,920 --> 00:12:13,240
he was kidnapped by Zhang Jinxi at the age of four

180
00:12:13,240 --> 00:12:15,280
and brought into this cell.

181
00:12:15,560 --> 00:12:17,040
He hasn't been out since.

182
00:12:17,440 --> 00:12:19,600
No one knows his real name

183
00:12:20,000 --> 00:12:21,060
or where he's from.

184
00:12:21,760 --> 00:12:24,440
However, Zhang Jinxi treats him a bit better.

185
00:12:25,160 --> 00:12:27,120
But he keeps telling him

186
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:30,020
that the outside world is dangerous,

187
00:12:30,160 --> 00:12:32,090
and only inside the cell is it safe.

188
00:12:33,920 --> 00:12:35,040
So he gave names

189
00:12:35,160 --> 00:12:37,600
to everything in the cell.

190
00:12:38,400 --> 00:12:40,200
He treated them as good friends.

191
00:12:40,920 --> 00:12:41,680
Shisan.

192
00:12:42,440 --> 00:12:44,370
Shisan, what are you playing with?

193
00:12:45,720 --> 00:12:46,720
Haitang, look.

194
00:12:47,440 --> 00:12:48,520
This is Xiaosi.

195
00:12:48,720 --> 00:12:49,760
This is Xiaoqi.

196
00:12:50,160 --> 00:12:51,490
Xiaowu went out to play.

197
00:12:51,560 --> 00:12:52,620
He'll be back soon.

198
00:12:53,680 --> 00:12:54,360
Thirteen,

199
00:12:54,680 --> 00:12:56,320
shall we play a game?

200
00:12:56,840 --> 00:12:57,840
What game?

201
00:12:58,800 --> 00:12:59,480
Look.

202
00:13:00,960 --> 00:13:03,040
This is a puppy.

203
00:13:04,160 --> 00:13:06,520
See how its mouth opens and closes?

204
00:13:06,520 --> 00:13:07,760
It loves to bark.

205
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:10,160
A puppy.

206
00:13:11,480 --> 00:13:13,480
It's all furry and fluffy.

207
00:13:13,920 --> 00:13:15,440
It loves being petted.

208
00:13:15,960 --> 00:13:17,040
Whenever someone pets it,

209
00:13:17,040 --> 00:13:18,700
it rolls around on the ground.

210
00:13:18,920 --> 00:13:19,840
Cute, isn't it?

211
00:13:23,320 --> 00:13:23,920
Look.

212
00:13:25,200 --> 00:13:27,060
Have you seen this animal before?

213
00:13:27,760 --> 00:13:28,400
No.

214
00:13:28,800 --> 00:13:30,160
It's a bird.

215
00:13:30,800 --> 00:13:32,840
It loves to be free every day,

216
00:13:32,840 --> 00:13:34,080
flying in the sky.

217
00:13:34,480 --> 00:13:35,840
It chirps and sings.

218
00:13:36,080 --> 00:13:37,210
It sounds so lovely.

219
00:13:37,240 --> 00:13:38,960
Then how do they sing?

220
00:13:40,360 --> 00:13:41,720
Cuckoo.

221
00:13:41,880 --> 00:13:43,280
Cuckoo.

222
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:45,320
Cuckoo.

223
00:13:50,560 --> 00:13:51,600
So, Thirteen,

224
00:13:52,440 --> 00:13:53,800
you must remember this.

225
00:13:54,600 --> 00:13:56,360
The world outside

226
00:13:56,360 --> 00:13:58,320
is not like you imagine.

227
00:13:59,040 --> 00:14:00,680
So when you get out,

228
00:14:01,320 --> 00:14:03,240
you will see that there are many,

229
00:14:03,240 --> 00:14:05,100
many beautiful things out there.

230
00:14:05,840 --> 00:14:07,360
The outside world.

231
00:14:08,600 --> 00:14:11,520
Cuckoo. Cuckoo.

232
00:14:12,440 --> 00:14:13,560
Cuckoo.

233
00:14:43,600 --> 00:14:44,520
Girls,

234
00:14:45,080 --> 00:14:46,240
you've suffered.

235
00:14:48,080 --> 00:14:49,120
This cellar

236
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:51,840
is indeed a bit cold and damp.

237
00:14:52,320 --> 00:14:53,000
However,

238
00:14:54,080 --> 00:14:55,160
this is also

239
00:14:56,080 --> 00:14:57,880
a nice, quiet place.

240
00:14:58,440 --> 00:14:59,160
Free from

241
00:14:59,320 --> 00:15:01,680
the chaos of the outside world.

242
00:15:03,360 --> 00:15:04,480
I know.

243
00:15:05,000 --> 00:15:06,360
You're all hungry.

244
00:15:06,560 --> 00:15:08,880
You were all born and raised by parents,

245
00:15:09,440 --> 00:15:10,840
suffering in here.

246
00:15:11,680 --> 00:15:13,000
My heart

247
00:15:13,840 --> 00:15:14,920
truly aches.

248
00:15:16,440 --> 00:15:17,240
So,

249
00:15:19,440 --> 00:15:20,360
today,

250
00:15:20,640 --> 00:15:21,370
I brought you

251
00:15:21,960 --> 00:15:23,160
some food.

252
00:16:47,120 --> 00:16:48,520
I knew

253
00:16:48,800 --> 00:16:50,200
you could do it.

254
00:16:52,520 --> 00:16:53,280
From now on,

255
00:16:53,800 --> 00:16:56,440
you'll come outside with me to live a good life.

256
00:17:11,400 --> 00:17:13,520
She just killed her best friend.

257
00:17:15,240 --> 00:17:16,319
In this world,

258
00:17:17,079 --> 00:17:18,720
there's no such thing as a free lunch.
